<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net">
  <diagram name="第 1 页" id="P2M3f-uy6UA4AIkSH_Ze">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1712" dy="919" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="OZyQ09rzj9GDgdih6PAc-1" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="factual knowledge / world knowledge" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="120" x="28" y="101" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OZyQ09rzj9GDgdih6PAc-2" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="procedure knowledge" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="120" x="28" y="361" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OZyQ09rzj9GDgdih6PAc-3" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="Judgement&amp;nbsp; knowledge" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="120" x="28" y="773" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OZyQ09rzj9GDgdih6PAc-4" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="feedback knowledge" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="120" x="887" y="365" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OZyQ09rzj9GDgdih6PAc-6" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;jv6v0&quot; data-start=&quot;130&quot; data-end=&quot;249&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;133&quot; data-end=&quot;249&quot;&gt;The alumina production chain runs from bauxite mining to alumina refining and then to primary aluminum smelting.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchor&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;ptxgs7&quot; data-start=&quot;251&quot; data-end=&quot;341&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;254&quot; data-end=&quot;341&quot;&gt;A specific copper smelter has a nameplate capacity of 500,000 metric tons per year.&lt;/strong&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1xbhg3o&quot; data-start=&quot;343&quot; data-end=&quot;477&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;346&quot; data-end=&quot;477&quot;&gt;The Shanghai Futures Exchange copper contract has defined deliverable grades, contract sizes, and approved delivery warehouses.&lt;/strong&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;15ig3ts&quot; data-start=&quot;479&quot; data-end=&quot;552&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;482&quot; data-end=&quot;552&quot;&gt;A major port suspended operations on July 10 because of a typhoon.&lt;/strong&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;12r1gjz&quot; data-start=&quot;554&quot; data-end=&quot;658&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;557&quot; data-end=&quot;658&quot;&gt;The reported polyethylene inventory in East China was 420,000 metric tons at the end of the week.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="122" width="550" x="182" y="34" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OZyQ09rzj9GDgdih6PAc-7" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;3w0f0f&quot; data-start=&quot;1986&quot; data-end=&quot;2129&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;6art7y&quot; data-start=&quot;1800&quot; data-end=&quot;1846&quot; class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer&quot;&gt;3. Judgmental Knowledge — Expert Heuristics&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1848&quot; data-end=&quot;1984&quot;&gt;Judgmental knowledge describes &lt;strong data-start=&quot;1879&quot; data-end=&quot;1983&quot;&gt;how experts make choices when evidence is incomplete, conflicting, or dependent on market conditions&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;1986&quot; data-end=&quot;2835&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;3w0f0f&quot; data-start=&quot;1986&quot; data-end=&quot;2129&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1989&quot; data-end=&quot;2129&quot;&gt;A newly announced production capacity should not be treated as effective supply until the plant has demonstrated stable operating rates.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1g9cjah&quot; data-start=&quot;2131&quot; data-end=&quot;2329&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2134&quot; data-end=&quot;2329&quot;&gt;A message from a plant operator may be more reliable for current operating conditions than a general industry-news article, but it may still be biased when discussing future production plans.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;u7gier&quot; data-start=&quot;2331&quot; data-end=&quot;2469&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2334&quot; data-end=&quot;2469&quot;&gt;A decline in visible inventory is less bullish when it is caused by transportation disruption rather than stronger end-user demand.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;obpxsg&quot; data-start=&quot;2471&quot; data-end=&quot;2644&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2474&quot; data-end=&quot;2644&quot;&gt;Production margins may be a weak supply signal for integrated producers because they optimize total-chain economics rather than the profitability of a single product.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;cukkqh&quot; data-start=&quot;2646&quot; data-end=&quot;2835&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2649&quot; data-end=&quot;2835&quot;&gt;When valuation appears cheap but supply is still accelerating, the supply driver may remain more important than historical valuation until there is evidence of a production response.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/li&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="310" width="550" x="174" y="768.9966666666667" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OZyQ09rzj9GDgdih6PAc-8" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;1xycsd9&quot; data-start=&quot;665&quot; data-end=&quot;712&quot; class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer&quot;&gt;2. Procedural Knowledge — Research Playbooks&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;714&quot; data-end=&quot;851&quot;&gt;Procedural knowledge describes &lt;strong data-start=&quot;745&quot; data-end=&quot;788&quot;&gt;how a research task should be performed&lt;/strong&gt;, including steps, checks, branches, and escalation conditions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;853&quot; data-end=&quot;1793&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;kc143q&quot; data-start=&quot;853&quot; data-end=&quot;1052&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;856&quot; data-end=&quot;1052&quot;&gt;To update the weekly supply-and-demand balance, first collect production, operating-rate, import, export, and inventory data, then reconcile the implied demand with observed inventory changes.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchor&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1ojhgv0&quot; data-start=&quot;1054&quot; data-end=&quot;1200&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1057&quot; data-end=&quot;1200&quot;&gt;When estimating supply losses from a plant shutdown, use the plant’s actual pre-shutdown operating rate rather than its nameplate capacity.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;ylnonn&quot; data-start=&quot;1202&quot; data-end=&quot;1386&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1205&quot; data-end=&quot;1386&quot;&gt;When two inventory sources disagree, compare their geographic coverage, reporting dates, sample composition, and revision history before deciding whether they can be reconciled.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1d3u8tc&quot; data-start=&quot;1388&quot; data-end=&quot;1545&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1391&quot; data-end=&quot;1545&quot;&gt;To evaluate whether port inventory is commercially available, exclude bonded, pledged, sold, quality-restricted, and operationally inaccessible stock.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;10cd9cc&quot; data-start=&quot;1547&quot; data-end=&quot;1793&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1550&quot; data-end=&quot;1793&quot;&gt;When analyzing the impact of a typhoon, check affected plants, ports, transportation routes, raw-material inventories, finished-goods inventories, alternative logistics, and expected disruption duration before updating the supply forecast.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="377" width="550" x="174" y="291.9966666666667" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OZyQ09rzj9GDgdih6PAc-9" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;div class=&quot;qMYqUG_convSearchResultHighlightRoot&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot; data-turn-id-container=&quot;request-6a53398a-8630-83ea-89a7-a352484381ce-1&quot; data-is-intersecting=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none [&amp;amp;:has([data-writing-block])&amp;gt;*]:pointer-events-auto R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; data-turn-id=&quot;request-6a53398a-8630-83ea-89a7-a352484381ce-1&quot; data-turn-id-container=&quot;request-6a53398a-8630-83ea-89a7-a352484381ce-1&quot; data-testid=&quot;conversation-turn-24&quot; data-turn=&quot;assistant&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;text-base my-auto mx-auto pb-15 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)&quot;&gt;&lt;div data-conversation-screenshot-content=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow&quot;&gt;&lt;div data-message-author-role=&quot;assistant&quot; data-message-id=&quot;d3d48e6b-7da1-48cc-97b0-f9d9f2a85dec&quot; data-turn-start-message=&quot;true&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; data-message-model-slug=&quot;gpt-5-6-thinking&quot; class=&quot;min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;amp;]:mt-1&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;wo71tj&quot; data-start=&quot;2842&quot; data-end=&quot;2903&quot; class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer&quot;&gt;4. Feedback Knowledge — Calibration and Learning Knowledge&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2905&quot; data-end=&quot;3044&quot; class=&quot;&quot;&gt;Feedback knowledge describes &lt;strong data-start=&quot;2934&quot; data-end=&quot;3043&quot;&gt;what the team learned from comparing previous data, methods, judgments, and forecasts with later outcomes&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;3046&quot; data-end=&quot;3938&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot; data-is-only-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1xezez8&quot; data-start=&quot;3046&quot; data-end=&quot;3218&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3049&quot; data-end=&quot;3218&quot;&gt;The initial weekly production estimate from a particular provider has historically been revised downward, so early releases should receive a lower confidence weight.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;g3pnd&quot; data-start=&quot;3220&quot; data-end=&quot;3376&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3223&quot; data-end=&quot;3376&quot;&gt;The team repeatedly overestimated supply losses from maintenance announcements because it used nameplate capacity rather than actual operating rates.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;94jme6&quot; data-start=&quot;3378&quot; data-end=&quot;3554&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3381&quot; data-end=&quot;3554&quot;&gt;In previous short typhoon disruptions, plants maintained production by using on-site inventories, so port closures shorter than three days had limited production impact.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;172b68i&quot; data-start=&quot;3556&quot; data-end=&quot;3732&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3559&quot; data-end=&quot;3732&quot;&gt;The team correctly predicted tighter physical supply, but the futures trade underperformed because the shortage had already been reflected in the nearby calendar spread.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;2ttige&quot; data-start=&quot;3734&quot; data-end=&quot;3938&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3737&quot; data-end=&quot;3938&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;The Agent frequently identifies the correct inventory table but confuses the observation date with the publication date, so temporal validation should be added to the workflow and Evaluation suite.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;mt-3 w-full empty:hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;text-center&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;pointer-events-none -mt-px h-px translate-y-(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom)&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="364" width="550" x="1032" y="292" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OZyQ09rzj9GDgdih6PAc-10" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;table&gt;&lt;thead&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;th&gt;Knowledge Type&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th&gt;Core Question&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th&gt;Suitable Representation&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th&gt;Primary Owner&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th&gt;Validation Method&lt;/th&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/thead&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Factual Knowledge&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;What does the market and industry landscape look like?&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Databases, domain models, and documentation&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Researchers and data owners&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Source verification, timestamp checks, and methodology or definition validation&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Procedural Knowledge&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;How should the research task be performed?&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Skills, workflows, and executable code&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Researchers define the methodology; engineers implement and operationalize it&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Verify whether the correct steps, checks, and escalation conditions were followed&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Judgmental Knowledge&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;How should decisions be made when information is incomplete, ambiguous, or conflicting?&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Conditional knowledge cards, expert heuristics, and historical cases&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Domain researchers&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Expert review, counterexamples, and validation of applicable conditions and exceptions&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Feedback Knowledge&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;How reliable have previous data, models, methods, and judgments been?&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Case libraries, evaluation datasets, and post-analysis review records&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Researchers, traders, and engineers jointly&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Outcome analysis, forecast-error analysis, and identification of systematic biases&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="404" width="550" x="935.0021883138022" y="750.997811686198" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
